details.description_text: A metal glass stand typically refers to a piece of furniture or a display stand made from metal, designed specifically to hold and showcase glassware. These stands are popular for organizing and displaying glass items such as drinking glasses, wine glasses, or decorative glassware. Metal glass stands come in various styles and designs, catering to different purposes and preferences. Here are some key aspects of metal glass stands:1. Material: Metal glass stands are primarily made from metals such as stainless steel, iron, or aluminum. These materials provide durability and stability to the stand, ensuring that it can support the weight of the glassware.2. Design: Metal glass stands come in a wide range of designs to suit different interior styles. Some stands have a minimalist and contemporary look, featuring sleek lines and a polished finish. Others may have ornate and decorative elements, making them suitable for traditional or vintage-themed settings. The design can also include shelves, hooks, or slots specifically crafted to hold glasses securely.3. Types: There are various types of metal glass stands, including countertop glass holders, wall-mounted glass racks, and freestanding glass display cabinets. Countertop stands are suitable for kitchen or bar counters, while wall-mounted racks are excellent space-saving solutions. Freestanding display cabinets provide a larger storage and display area and are often used in commercial settings such as restaurants or wine shops.4. Capacity: Metal glass stands come in different sizes and capacities, accommodating a varying number of glassware items. Some stands are designed for a specific type of glass, such as wine glasses, while others are more versatile and can hold different types of glassware.5. Maintenance: Metal glass stands are relatively easy to clean and maintain. Regular dusting and occasional cleaning with a mild metal cleaner or a damp cloth are usually sufficient to keep the stand in good condition.Buy Metal & Plastic Glass Stand through online from iferi.com in BangladeshDetailsSize: 8" x 10"Material: Metal & Plastic Made in China

details.description_text: Material: Stainless steel Package includes: 1x Kitchen Storage ShelfSpecification:Product Name: Kitchen Storage ShelfMaterial: Stainless steelColor: BlackStyle: Bowl Rack / Dish Rack / Pot Rack / Fan-shaped Hanging Basket / 40cm Hanging Rod / Chopstick Rack / 25cm Hanging Basket / 35cm Hanging Basket / 40cm Hanging Basket(Please let us know the Style you’d like.You can LEAVE THE EMAIL ON YOUR PAYPAL NOTE to tell us.)Features:1.These kitchen utensils can make good use of the dead corner of the kitchen to keep the sink area clean and tidy, so that you can do any cooking preparation work.2.25/35/40cm rectangular and fan-shaped Hanging Basket can be used in the kitchen to store seasoning bottles, or in the bathroom to store shampoo, conditioner, shower gel and other toiletries.3.40cm Hanging Rod can be used to hang other kitchen accessories, such as spatula, etc., to make your counter cleaner and cleaner.4.Made of stainless steel, so it not easy to bend or break, rust-resistant, corrosion-resistant and durable.-Installation without punching:1.Wipe the wall clean, tear off the protective film of the base, and then connect the frame to the base, put it on the wall, and then mark the position with a pen.2.Take off the base and the frame separately, apply nail-free glue on the base, do not apply too much.3.Put the base on the wall in the marked position, press firmly, and attach the auxiliary anti-skid sticker.4.After waiting 72 hours for the base glue to dry completely, hang the rack and use it.-Perforated Installation:1.Wipe the wall clean, tear off the protective film of the base, and then connect the frame to the base, put it on the wall, and then mark the position with a pen.2.Use an 8mm drill to drill holes at the marked locations.3.Knock the expansion bolt into the hole, then fix the base to the wall with screws, and tighten the screws.4.Hang the rack to use.

details.description_text: A metal glass stand typically refers to a piece of furniture or a display stand made from metal, designed specifically to hold and showcase glassware. These stands are popular for organizing and displaying glass items such as drinking glasses, wine glasses, or decorative glassware. Metal glass stands come in various styles and designs, catering to different purposes and preferences. Here are some key aspects of metal glass stands:1. Material: Metal glass stands are primarily made from metals such as stainless steel, iron, or aluminum. These materials provide durability and stability to the stand, ensuring that it can support the weight of the glassware.2. Design: Metal glass stands come in a wide range of designs to suit different interior styles. Some stands have a minimalist and contemporary look, featuring sleek lines and a polished finish. Others may have ornate and decorative elements, making them suitable for traditional or vintage-themed settings. The design can also include shelves, hooks, or slots specifically crafted to hold glasses securely.3. Types: There are various types of metal glass stands, including countertop glass holders, wall-mounted glass racks, and freestanding glass display cabinets. Countertop stands are suitable for kitchen or bar counters, while wall-mounted racks are excellent space-saving solutions. Freestanding display cabinets provide a larger storage and display area and are often used in commercial settings such as restaurants or wine shops.4. Capacity: Metal glass stands come in different sizes and capacities, accommodating a varying number of glassware items. Some stands are designed for a specific type of glass, such as wine glasses, while others are more versatile and can hold different types of glassware.5. Maintenance: Metal glass stands are relatively easy to clean and maintain. Regular dusting and occasional cleaning with a mild metal cleaner or a damp cloth are usually sufficient to keep the stand in good condition.Buy Metal & Plastic Glass Stand through online from iferi.com in BangladeshDetailsSize: 8" x 10"Material: Metal & Plastic Made in China

details.description_text: Material: Stainless steel Package includes: 1x Kitchen Storage ShelfSpecification:Product Name: Kitchen Storage ShelfMaterial: Stainless steelColor: BlackStyle: Bowl Rack / Dish Rack / Pot Rack / Fan-shaped Hanging Basket / 40cm Hanging Rod / Chopstick Rack / 25cm Hanging Basket / 35cm Hanging Basket / 40cm Hanging Basket(Please let us know the Style you’d like.You can LEAVE THE EMAIL ON YOUR PAYPAL NOTE to tell us.)Features:1.These kitchen utensils can make good use of the dead corner of the kitchen to keep the sink area clean and tidy, so that you can do any cooking preparation work.2.25/35/40cm rectangular and fan-shaped Hanging Basket can be used in the kitchen to store seasoning bottles, or in the bathroom to store shampoo, conditioner, shower gel and other toiletries.3.40cm Hanging Rod can be used to hang other kitchen accessories, such as spatula, etc., to make your counter cleaner and cleaner.4.Made of stainless steel, so it not easy to bend or break, rust-resistant, corrosion-resistant and durable.-Installation without punching:1.Wipe the wall clean, tear off the protective film of the base, and then connect the frame to the base, put it on the wall, and then mark the position with a pen.2.Take off the base and the frame separately, apply nail-free glue on the base, do not apply too much.3.Put the base on the wall in the marked position, press firmly, and attach the auxiliary anti-skid sticker.4.After waiting 72 hours for the base glue to dry completely, hang the rack and use it.-Perforated Installation:1.Wipe the wall clean, tear off the protective film of the base, and then connect the frame to the base, put it on the wall, and then mark the position with a pen.2.Use an 8mm drill to drill holes at the marked locations.3.Knock the expansion bolt into the hole, then fix the base to the wall with screws, and tighten the screws.4.Hang the rack to use.

product_title: Rectangular Glass Holder - 6 Holder

detail.name: Rectangular Glass Holder - 6 Holder

details.description_text: A metal glass stand typically refers to a piece of furniture or a display stand made from metal, designed specifically to hold and showcase glassware. These stands are popular for organizing and displaying glass items such as drinking glasses, wine glasses, or decorative glassware. Metal glass stands come in various styles and designs, catering to different purposes and preferences. Here are some key aspects of metal glass stands:1. Material: Metal glass stands are primarily made from metals such as stainless steel, iron, or aluminum. These materials provide durability and stability to the stand, ensuring that it can support the weight of the glassware.2. Design: Metal glass stands come in a wide range of designs to suit different interior styles. Some stands have a minimalist and contemporary look, featuring sleek lines and a polished finish. Others may have ornate and decorative elements, making them suitable for traditional or vintage-themed settings. The design can also include shelves, hooks, or slots specifically crafted to hold glasses securely.3. Types: There are various types of metal glass stands, including countertop glass holders, wall-mounted glass racks, and freestanding glass display cabinets. Countertop stands are suitable for kitchen or bar counters, while wall-mounted racks are excellent space-saving solutions. Freestanding display cabinets provide a larger storage and display area and are often used in commercial settings such as restaurants or wine shops.4. Capacity: Metal glass stands come in different sizes and capacities, accommodating a varying number of glassware items. Some stands are designed for a specific type of glass, such as wine glasses, while others are more versatile and can hold different types of glassware.5. Maintenance: Metal glass stands are relatively easy to clean and maintain. Regular dusting and occasional cleaning with a mild metal cleaner or a damp cloth are usually sufficient to keep the stand in good condition.Buy Metal & Plastic Glass Stand through online from iferi.com in BangladeshDetailsSize: 8" x 10"Material: Metal & PlasticMade in China

details.description_text: A metal glass stand typically refers to a piece of furniture or a display stand made from metal, designed specifically to hold and showcase glassware. These stands are popular for organizing and displaying glass items such as drinking glasses, wine glasses, or decorative glassware. Metal glass stands come in various styles and designs, catering to different purposes and preferences. Here are some key aspects of metal glass stands:1. Material: Metal glass stands are primarily made from metals such as stainless steel, iron, or aluminum. These materials provide durability and stability to the stand, ensuring that it can support the weight of the glassware.2. Design: Metal glass stands come in a wide range of designs to suit different interior styles. Some stands have a minimalist and contemporary look, featuring sleek lines and a polished finish. Others may have ornate and decorative elements, making them suitable for traditional or vintage-themed settings. The design can also include shelves, hooks, or slots specifically crafted to hold glasses securely.3. Types: There are various types of metal glass stands, including countertop glass holders, wall-mounted glass racks, and freestanding glass display cabinets. Countertop stands are suitable for kitchen or bar counters, while wall-mounted racks are excellent space-saving solutions. Freestanding display cabinets provide a larger storage and display area and are often used in commercial settings such as restaurants or wine shops.4. Capacity: Metal glass stands come in different sizes and capacities, accommodating a varying number of glassware items. Some stands are designed for a specific type of glass, such as wine glasses, while others are more versatile and can hold different types of glassware.5. Maintenance: Metal glass stands are relatively easy to clean and maintain. Regular dusting and occasional cleaning with a mild metal cleaner or a damp cloth are usually sufficient to keep the stand in good condition.Buy Metal & Plastic Glass Stand through online from iferi.com in BangladeshDetailsSize: 8" x 10"Material: Metal & Plastic Made in China
